Series II: Correspondence

langmaterial

English

Scope and Content

Subseries A: Paper-based Correspondence is organized alphabetically by correspondent; correspondence from unidentified or partially identified correspondents is organized by date and follows the last alphabetical entry; a folder containing the early correspondence of Richard Hell's parents (Ernest Meyers and Carolyn Hodgson) annotated by his mother follows and fan mail is collected at the end of the series.
